---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  locale="ja"
  title="お問い合わせ | Contact"
  currentPath="/ja/contact"
  description="BMTechの製品で構築をはじめませんか？製品に関するお問い合わせ、技術サポートなどは、こちらから直接チームへご連絡ください。"
  ogTitle="お問い合わせ | Contact"
  ogDescription="BMTechの製品で構築をはじめませんか？製品に関するお問い合わせ、技術サポートなどは、こちらから直接チームへご連絡ください。"
  ogImage="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6a0c84e4593078e8f088bb7c/6a0fe4369f79f753573f39c8_8b94941eb69acb8d526938741fe02663_sign-gemini-trans.png"
  webflowPageId="6a1f15d68331060a67be7820"
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <style>html.w-mod-js:not(.w-mod-ix3) :is(.linked-nav-logo) {visibility: hidden !important;}</style>
  </Fragment>

  <Fragment slot="scripts">
    <script src="/js/contact-form.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
  </Fragment>

  <div class="main-wrapper">
    <section class="hero-section small overlay-dark">
      <div class="w-layout-blockcontainer hero-container overlay-dark-2 w-container">
        <h1 data-w-id="cffab803-26ef-6867-3cb2-f5ad37876f0b" style="opacity:0" class="display-lg banner">お問い合わせ</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="overlay overlay-dark-4"></div><img sizes="(max-width: 1919px) 100vw, 1920px" srcset="/images/zbynek-burival-V4ZYJZJ3W4M-unsplash-p-500.jpg 500w, /images/zbynek-burival-V4ZYJZJ3W4M-unsplash-p-800.jpg 800w, /images/zbynek-burival-V4ZYJZJ3W4M-unsplash-p-1080.jpg 1080w, /images/zbynek-burival-V4ZYJZJ3W4M-unsplash-p-1600.jpg 1600w, /images/zbynek-burival-V4ZYJZJ3W4M-unsplash.jpg 1920w" alt="Solar panels in a field" loading="lazy" src="/images/zbynek-burival-V4ZYJZJ3W4M-unsplash.jpg" class="image-2 overlay-dark-5">
    </section>
    <div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container w-container">
      <div class="contact-wrap">
        <div class="contact-left">
          <h2 data-w-id="31f30811-b254-762b-b994-04dbeda6df14" class="contact-h2">お気軽にご相談ください</h2>
          <p data-w-id="31f30811-b254-762b-b994-04dbeda6df16" class="body-txt gray">ご質問、製品に関するお問い合わせ、コラボレーションのご相談など、下記フォームまたはメールよりお気軽にご連絡ください。担当者より折り返しご連絡いたします。</p>
          <div data-w-id="31f30811-b254-762b-b994-04dbeda6df28" class="contact-info-item _1st">
            <p class="contact-info-title">本社</p>
            <p class="section-content">Suite 325, 1255 W 15th St<br>Plano, TX 75075, USA</p>
          </div>
          <div data-w-id="31f30811-b254-762b-b994-04dbeda6df2d" style="opacity:0" class="contact-info-item">
            <p class="contact-info-title">工場</p>
            <p class="section-content">Suite 103, 789 N Grover Rd<br>Richardson, TX 75081, USA</p>
          </div>
          <div data-w-id="31f30811-b254-762b-b994-04dbeda6df2d" class="contact-info-item">
            <p class="contact-info-title"><strong class="contact-info-title">メールアドレス</strong></p>
            <a href="mailto:info@bmtech.com?subject=Inquiry" class="section-content link">info@bmtech.com</a>
          </div>
          <!-- <div data-w-id="d1b609b2-14cf-2074-c3a7-c99485231387" class="contact-info-item">
            <p class="contact-info-title">電話番号</p>
            <a href="" class="section-content link"></a>
          </div> -->
          <div data-w-id="31f30811-b254-762b-b994-04dbeda6df2d" class="contact-info-item">
            <p class="contact-info-title">SNS</p>
            <ul role="list" class="social-list">
              <li class="social-item">
                <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/battery-management-technology-corporation" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="social-link-two w-inline-block"><img src="/images/linkedin.svg" loading="lazy" alt="Icon" class="social-icon"></a>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <a data-w-id="31f30811-b254-762b-b994-04dbeda6df2d" href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/1255+W+15th+St,+Plano,+TX+75075/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="map-link-2 map-link w-inline-block"><img src="/images/map-md.png" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 923px) 100vw, 923px" srcset="/images/a02cef54fca28df437cab64ae64b2a51_map-md-p-500.png 500w, /images/a02cef54fca28df437cab64ae64b2a51_map-md-p-800.png 800w, /images/map-md.png 923w" alt="Map" class="map-2 map"></a>
        </div>
        <div data-w-id="31f30811-b254-762b-b994-04dbeda6df32" class="form-main">
          <form id="email-form" name="email-form" action="https://r8gtx7aav7.execute-api.us-east-2.amazonaws.com/contact" method="post" class="form js-contact-form" data-locale="ja">
            <div aria-hidden="true" style="position:absolute;left:-10000px;width:1px;height:1px;overflow:hidden;"><label for="website">ウェブサイト</label><input type="text" id="website" name="website" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off"></div>
            <div class="single-block"><label for="name" class="input-label">お名前 *</label><input class="form-input w-input" maxlength="256" name="name" placeholder="例：山田 太郎" type="text" id="name" autocomplete="name" required></div>
            <div class="single-block"><label for="email" class="input-label">メールアドレス *</label><input class="form-input w-input" maxlength="256" name="email" placeholder="例：example@domain.com" type="email" id="email" autocomplete="email" required></div>
            <div class="single-block"><label for="phone" class="input-label">電話番号</label><input class="form-input w-input" maxlength="50" name="phone" placeholder="例：+81-90-1234-5678" type="tel" id="phone" autocomplete="tel"></div>
            <div class="single-block"><label for="field" class="input-label">件名 *</label>
              <div class="form-input select"><select id="field" name="subject" required class="form-select w-select">
                  <option value="" disabled selected>選択してください</option>
                  <option value="Inquiry">一般のお問い合わせ</option>
                  <option value="Career">採用情報</option>
                  <option value="Security">セキュリティ関連</option>
                  <option value="Other">その他</option>
                </select></div>
            </div>
            <div class="single-block"><label for="message" class="input-label">お問い合わせ内容 *</label><textarea required placeholder="内容を入力してください" minlength="10" maxlength="5000" id="message" name="message" class="form-input message w-input"></textarea></div><input type="submit" data-wait="送信中..." class="btn-submit btn-primary w-button" value="送信">
          </form>
          <div class="success-message" role="status" aria-live="polite" tabindex="-1" hidden>
            <div>送信が完了しました。お問い合わせいただき、ありがとうございます。</div>
          </div>
          <div class="error-message" role="alert" aria-live="assertive" tabindex="-1" hidden>
            <div>エラーが発生しました。お手数ですが、もう一度お試しください。</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
